="no"></iframe></div><p> Channels 或多或少是<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/telegram-channel-ads-192249765.html">竞争对手同名聊天应用 Telegram</a>上类似功能的副本。今年早些时候，Meta 在 Instagram 上<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-is-bringing-telegram-like-channels-to-instagram-184054107.html?guccounter=1">推出了</a>广播频道，让创作者可以像 WhatsApp 用户一样将<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://about.fb.com/news/2023/02/instagram-broadcast-channels-creators-deepen-connections-with-followers/">更新流式</a>传输到他们的粉丝的收件箱中。该功能可以比作时事通讯，事实上，它<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.androidpolice.com/whatsapp-channels-rumored-newsletter-tool/">可能在开发时就被称为</a>时事通讯（或者后者可能会在以后作为单独的功能出现）。</p><p> WhatsApp 的发展已经远远超出了它作为一个简单的消息应用程序的初衷。 Meta 最近增加了<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-now-lets-you-use-your-account-on-multiple-phones-163158921.html">在多个设备上使用一个帐户的</a>功能，这在以前不仅是不可能的，而且在您更换手机时可能会造成麻烦。该公司还更新了群聊，同时增加了投票、购物等功能。</p><p>该公司表示，新功能并未广泛推出，而是从“领先的全球组织和哥伦比亚和新加坡的精选组织”开始。它将在“未来几个月”到达更多国家和用户。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/whatsapps-new-channels-feature-lets-accounts-send-one-way-updates-to-followers-090843232.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/whatsapps-new-channels-feature-lets-accounts-send-one-way-updates-to-followers-090843232.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> fe7cc50f-3d24-4602-a469-8c37525d1e62</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 08 Jun 2023 09:08:43 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686226846</ingested><modified> 2023-06-08T12:20:50+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1107" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/c0730080-05f6-11ee-aae9-7298848385ab" width="1868"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1107" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/c0730080-05f6-11ee-aae9-7298848385ab" width="1868"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[WhatsApp]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Three mockups of WhatsApp screens display the new WhatsApp Channels feature for private one-way broadcasts to followers.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[WhatsApp]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>